---
title: Grilled Cowboy-Style Chicken and Bacon Burgers with Stone Fruit and Potato Wedges
description: With smoky bacon and seasoned tender chicken on buttered buns with a zesty mayo spread and homemade cowboy candy (a condiment made of sliced jalapeño simmered in a sweet and tangy syrup), this supper truly has it all.
